'''The Tolkien Calendar 1991''' was published by [[Seckja Tolkienowska]], the [[Polish Tolkien Society]] and was edited by [[Andrzej Kowalski]]. The calendar contains black and white illustrations by [[Małgorzata Pudlik]] and [[Aleksandra Kosciuszuk]].

* Dimensions: 8 1/4 x 11 3/4 inches
* Unbound
